            <uicontrol>Filter</uicontrol> to define the styling for a condition set like
        this:</p></sectiondiv>
      <p><image href="../img/ditaval_filter_flag.png" placement="inline"/></p>
      <p>will render the styling of the profiled content in <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode to
        look like this:</p>
      <p><image href="../img/ditaval_render_author.png" placement="inline"/></p>
      <p>and will render the styling in the <xref href="dita-maps-manager.dita#dita-maps-manager"
            ><uicontrol>DITA Maps Manager</uicontrol> view</xref> to look like this:</p>
      <p><image href="../img/ditaval_render_dmm.png" placement="inline"/></p>
    </section>
  </body>
